                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When an alchemical golem takes physical damage from a critical hit or is affected by a <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Shatter]{Shatter}</em> spell, one glass chamber within its body shatters, spewing alchemical liquid in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5].</p>\n<p>Roll on the alchemical chambers list to determine which one shatters - all creatures within a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5] are affected by the elixir in the randomly rolled alchemical chamber, and these creatures may forego their Reflex saves against the effect if they wish.</p>"
